{{Nihongo|'''''Bikini Warriors'''''|ビキニ・ウォリアーズ|Bikini Woriāzu}} is a Japanese media franchise. It primarily consists of a series of fantasy [[model figure|figure]]s created by [[Hobby Japan]] and [[Megahouse]], featuring character designs from multiple artists including [[Rei Hiroe]], [[Hisasi]], [[Saitom]] and [[Tony Taka|Tony]]. A 12-episode [[anime]] television series based on the setting aired between July 7 and September 22, 2015. A [[manga]] series and a video game have also been announced.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-05-16/bikini-warriors-fantasy-figure-series-gets-tv-anime-project-in-july/.88235|title=''Bikini Warriors'' Fantasy Figure Series Gets TV Anime Project in July|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=May 16, 2015|accessdate=May 16, 2015}}</ref>

==Plot summary==
The series consists of a sequence of short stories describing the (mis-) adventures of four female adventurers in a fantasy world teeming with dangerous monsters and hostile magicians. Clad in generously cut-out, yet effective bikini-type armor, the four women must learn to overcome the hazards of their world to meet their living expenses while at the same time trying to get comfortable with the idea of exposing too much of their curvaceous physiques.

==Characters==

===Main characters===
;{{Nihongo|Fighter|ファイター|Faitā}}
:{{voiced by|[[Yōko Hikasa]]|[[Felecia Angelle]]}}
:A redhaired, somewhat impulsive and stubborn woman, and the party's leader. She is also the daughter of a legendary warrior who saved the country in the past.
;{{Nihongo|Paladin|パラディン|Paradin}}
:{{voiced by|[[Kana Ueda]]|[[Alexis Tipton]]}}
:A beautiful blonde woman who (most unbecoming to her [[Paladin (Dungeons & Dragons)|vocation]]) harbors closeted sexual desires.
;{{Nihongo|Mage|メイジ|Meiji}}
:{{voiced by|[[Ai Kakuma]]|[[Sarah Wiedenheft]]}}
:The youngest and most timid member of the adventure party, the [[Magician (fantasy)|Mage]] is a petite purple-haired girl skilled in the art of sorcery.
;{{Nihongo|Dark Elf|ダークエルフ|Dākuerufu}}
:{{voiced by|[[Chiaki Takahashi (actress)|Chiaki Takahashi]]|Dawn M. Bennett}}
:A member of the [[Drow (Dungeons & Dragons)|Dark Elf]] race who assists the party with a versatile combination of combat and magic-using skills. Initially quite haughty when she first joined, she has shed much of her attitude as the four of them have kept adventuring together.

