==Media==

===Anime===
An [[anime]] television series based on the manga by studios [[Feel (company)|Feel]] and PRA aired between July 7 and September 22, 2015. [[Madman Entertainment]] secured streaming rights in Australia & New Zealand, who simulcasted the series on AnimeLab.<ref>[https://www.animelab.com/blog/animelab-simulcast-line-up-for-summer-2015/ AnimeLab Simulcast Line-Up For Summer 2015]</ref> [[Funimation]] announced they had secured streaming rights within North America, and simulcasted the series on their service.

