{{Infobox venue |name=Tsuyama Stadium |nickname= |native_name=岡山県津山陸上競技場 |native_name_lang= |fullname= |former names= |logo_image= |logo_caption= |image=Tsuyama1.jpg |image_size= |image_alt= |caption= |pushpin_map= |pushpin_mapsize= |pushpin_map_caption= |pushpin_label_position= |address= |location={{flagicon|Japan}} [[Tsuyama]], [[Okayama Prefecture|Okayama]], [[Japan]] |coordinates= |type= |genre= |broke_ground= |built= |opened=1994 |renovated= |expanded= |closed= |demolished= |owner=[[Okayama Prefecture]] |operator= |surface= |scoreboard= |production= |cost= |architect= |builder= |project_manager= |structural engineer= |services engineer= |general_contractor= |main_contractors= |seating_type= |capacity=10,000 |suites= |record_attendance= |dimensions= |field_shape= |acreage= |volume= |tenants= |embedded= |website= |publictransit= }} {{nihongo|'''Tsuyama Stadium'''|岡山県津山陸上競技場}} is an [[Sport of athletics|athletic]] [[stadium]] in [[Tsuyama]], [[Okayama Prefecture|Okayama]], [[Japan]].
